overview: For the first time in Wicked Pictures history all of Wicked's contract SUPERSTARS come together in one incredible movie. Alektra, Jessica, Kaylani, Kristen, Mikayla and Stormy as you've never seen them before ... The result is the HOUSE OF WICKED, an amazing combination of beauty, style, and raw sexual energy. These ravishing beauties slide into their own brand of Wicked Couture, and work it for the cameras like no one else can ... Gothic, Club Wear, Asian Flair, Skater Chic, Cowgirl, Prep School, or Heavy Metal, each of which sets the stage for the WICKED GIRLS to do what they do best ... and they've never looked more amazing doing it. Once you've entered the HOUSE OF WICKED you'll never want to leave ..
tagline: Starring Wicked Pictures Exclusive Contract Stars TOGETHER FOR THE FIRST TIME
title: House of Wicked
